ed="T" n="0777c13"/><persName key="A010534">釋玄策</persName>，俗姓<name>魯</name>，<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName>人也。幼隨父商估，赴<lb
ed="T" n="0777c14"/><placeName key="PL000000014411">天台山</placeName>光明會，乃<date from-iso="+0581-03-06" key="j19333311946884" to-iso="+0618-04-15"><name>隋</name>朝</date><persName key="A001301">智顗<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>立教，年別<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1578"/><lb
ed="T" n="0777c15"/>九月，遠近州邑黑白二眾鳩聚。<persName key="A010534">策</persName>覩殊異，遂<lb
ed="T" n="0777c16"/><anchor xml:id="beg0777sgsz12"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0777sgsz12"/><placeName key="PL000000014691">禪林寺</placeName><persName key="A010536">智廣<roleName>師</roleName></persName>下出家。遊方見<placeName key="PL000000018627">江西</placeName><persName key="A003623">大<lb
ed="T" n="0777c17"/>寂</persName>，頓開翳障。及遍參問，覩<placeName key="PL000000026508"><placeName>黃陂</placeName><placeName>九井山</placeName></placeName>奇<lb
ed="T" n="0777c18"/>秀，乃結茅為舍，學侶若蟬之走明也。或慰<lb
ed="T" n="0777c19"/><persName key="A010534">策</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010534">師</ref>之耐寂<anchor xml:id="beg0777004"/>寞<anchor xml:id="end0777004"/>如此乎？」<persName key="A010534">策</persName>曰：「致道者<lb
ed="T" n="0777c20"/>忘心矣，<ref type="person" target="#A010534">吾</ref>樂甚哉。」以<date from-iso="+0854-02-05" key="j20330132033367" to-iso="+0855-01-25"><name>大中</name>八年</date>現疾而滅。<lb
ed="T" n="0777c21"/>續勅謚大師曰<persName key="A010534">圓寂</persName>，塔名<placeName key="PL000000057043">智覺</placeName>焉。</p>
